Class MXEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matrix.androidsdk.listeners.MXEventListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMXEventListener

    public class MXEventListener
extends Object
implements IMXEventListener
    A no-op class implementing IMXEventListener so listeners can just implement the methods that they require.
